02:48:41.389 --> 02:48:44.888
Petnaest! Šesnaest!
-Sedamnaest!

02:48:52.691 --> 02:48:54.601
Merry!

02:49:36.609 --> 02:49:38.401
Legolase!

02:50:00.800 --> 02:50:03.172
Trideset tri, trideset četiri.

02:50:50.265 --> 02:50:54.967
Ipak se računa kao jedan!
Hajde, onda. Hajde!

02:51:38.687 --> 02:51:41.522
Poznam tvoje lice...

02:51:43.306 --> 02:51:45.227
Éowyn.

02:51:47.821 --> 02:51:50.193
