02:51:51.283 --> 02:51:55.224
Ne. Ne.

02:51:57.231 --> 02:52:03.409
Spasit ću te.
-Već jesi.

02:52:07.090 --> 02:52:12.709
Éowyn... Moje
je tijelo slomljeno.

02:52:17.720 --> 02:52:20.222
Moraš me pustiti.

02:52:26.087 --> 02:52:28.682
Idem svojim ocima,

02:52:30.133 --> 02:52:36.782
