02:53:55.445 --> 02:53:57.635
Smatram vašu prisegu ispunjenom.

02:53:58.860 --> 02:54:02.861
Idite. Počivajte.

02:54:46.162 --> 02:54:48.101
Merry.

02:54:48.675 --> 02:54:52.011
Ne!

02:54:55.556 --> 02:54:58.319
Ne!

02:55:21.968 --> 02:55:29.776
<i>"Uzdišeš i okrećeš se</i>

02:55:29.913 --> 02:55:38.880
<i>Duboko u srcu
