03:19:39.506 --> 03:19:40.913
Ne želim.

03:19:56.971 --> 03:20:01.138
Povucimo se. Povucimo se!

03:20:13.341 --> 03:20:15.402
Otišlo je, gospodine Frodo.

03:20:17.303 --> 03:20:22.869
